  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> in half (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon)</p><p>Top, tail and chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Cut your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into quarters, keeping the skin on and root attached</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finley chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped veg </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to a bowl with a large drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>seasoned</strong> <strong>veg </strong>to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> sausages </strong>to the opposite side of the tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min until the sausages are golden and cooked through and the veg is starting to brown</p><p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Add your<strong> couscous</strong> to the bowl, then cover and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to a pot over a medium-high heat</p><p>Bring to the boil, then reduce the heat to very low and cook for approx. 2-3 min or until it turns into a runny glaze that coats the back of a spoon</p><p>Tip: Watch the pan like a hawk to make sure it doesn't burn!</p><p>Once done, remove the pot from the heat and set aside until serving – this is your <strong>balsamic glaze</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/354.-step5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
