      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Mix the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>roasted pepper</strong>, <strong>roasted onion petals</strong> and <strong>chopped basil</strong> through the couscous – this is your <strong>roasted veg couscous</strong></p><p>Drizzle generously with <strong>olive oil</strong> and taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p>",
